 2023-11082023-11-03FIN, MINT
ActRoyal Canadian Mint Act
SubjectOrder Authorizing the Issue, Specifying the Characteristics and Determining the Design of Six Circulation Coins (His Majesty King Charles III)
PrecisOrder authorizing the Royal Canadian Mint to produce a SIX (6) CIRCULATION COINS (5-cent, 10-cent, 25-cent, 50-cent, $1, $2) featuring the effigy of His Majesty KING CHARLES III as the central element of the obverse and to combine the new obverse design with the existing reverse designs of Canada’s circulation coins.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2023-0231 Publication Date: 2023-11-22
